  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2009-0311<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2009-02-26</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nAttendu que l'honorable Robert N. Weekes, juge de la Cour supérieure de justice de l’Ontario, ayant atteint l’âge de cinquante-cinq ans, ayant au moins dix ans d’ancienneté dans la magistrature et ayant choisi une retraite anticipée avec une pension immédiate, a donné sa démission, laquelle prend effet le 1<sup>er</sup> février 2009,\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nÀ ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil :\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<em>a</em>) accepte la démission de l'honorable Robert N. Weekes;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<em>b</em>) en vertu du paragraphe 43.1(1) de la <em>Loi sur les juges</em>, lui accorde, à titre viager, une pension annuelle de 165 672,19 $, payable à compter du 1<sup>er</sup> février 2009.\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nWhereas the Honourable Robert N. Weekes, a Judge of the Superior Court of Justice in and for the Province of Ontario, who has attained the age of fifty-five years, who has continued in judicial office for at least ten years and who has elected early retirement with an immediate annuity, has tendered his resignation effective February 1, 2009; \n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nTherefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, hereby\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(<em>a</em>) accepts the resignation of the Honourable Robert N. Weekes; and\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(<em>b</em>) pursuant to subsection 43.1(1) of the <em>Judges Act</em>, hereby grants him an annuity of $165,672.19, commencing on February 1, 2009, and continuing during his life.\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<u><strong>&nbsp;</strong></u>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<u><strong>&nbsp;</strong></u>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<u><strong>&nbsp;</strong></u>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<strong>EXPLANATORY NOTE</strong>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThis Order in Council prescribes:\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThat Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice,  accept the resignation of the Honourable Robert N. Weekes and, pursuant to paragraph 43.1(1) of the <em>Judges Act</em>, she hereby  grants him an annuity of $165,672.19 to commence on February 1, 2009, and to continue during his life.\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<strong>NOTE EXPLICATIVE</strong>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCe décret prescrit:\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nQue sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil accepte la démission de l'honorable Robert N. Weekes et, en vertu de l'alinéa 43.1(1) de la <em>Loi sur les juges</em>, elle accorde à ce dernier une  pension  de 165 672,19 $, à compter du 1<sup>er</sup> février 2009 et qu'elle continue durant sa vie.\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<u><strong>&nbsp;</strong></u>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong>\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
